    "date": "2020-01-23T17:17:27Z",
    "text": "Safe Water for Military Families Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to ensure that, no later than January 1, 2029, it uses only non-fluorinated firefighting foam, which does not contain a perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substance (PFAS) with at least one fully fluorinated carbon atom.\n\nDOD shall study best practices to clean up ground contaminated by PFAS substances."
